
# NtcConvert

Arduino / PlatformIO library for NTC temperature conversion.

## Features
- Input: ADC value (0..4095)
- Output: Temperature in °C
- NTC: 10k @ 25°C, Beta 3435
- Divider: 33k (top) / NTC (bottom)
- Tested with MCP3202 (12-bit)

## Usage

```cpp
#include <NtcConvert.h>

int adc = readAdc();
float t = NtcConvert(adc);
